      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs beautifully, the interior is super comfy, and it has plenty of life left for all your road trips and daily commutes. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love driving it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will really enjoy it!",
