      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54B32 atmospheric inline-six. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. Recent technical updates include a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustment, optimizing the valvetrain for its 8,000 RPM redline. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' status, the powertrain remains a benchmark of German engineering, benefiting from a recent cooling system refresh and fresh bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. This is a driver-spec machine ready for the apex.",
